## Testing Authentication

```ruby
test "requires login for new" do
  get new_article_url
  assert_redirected_to login_url
end

test "requires login for create" do
  post articles_url, params: { article: { title: "Test" } }
  assert_redirected_to login_url
end

test "allows access when logged in" do
  sign_in_as @user
  get new_article_url
  assert_response :success
end
```

